//[Reference] 'A few years ago, I took my name out of the running for mayor.'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10000100=数年前、町長に立候補するのを辞めたんです。
//[Reference] 'I felt like my time had passed, that I had no more to contribute.'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10000200=もう役割は果たし、これ以上できることも無いと思っていました。
//[Reference] 'To be honest, I really only wanted to retire and live in peace.'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10000300=正直、とにかく引退してのんびり過ごしたかったんです。
//[Reference] 'Everyone voted for me anyway.'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10000400=でもみんな私に投票したんですよ。
//[Reference] 'I took it as a sign and redoubled my efforts!'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10000500=それでまた頑張ることにしたんです！
//[Reference] 'I long for retirement again...but I know it will just be snatched away.'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10000600=再び引退することを切望しているのですが…それが叶わぬ夢であることも分かっています。
//[Reference] 'As long as there is no one to follow after me, they'll just re-elect me every time...'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10000700=後任が現れない限り、毎回私が再選させられるでしょうし…
//[Reference] '^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! Thinking on it a bit more...'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10000800=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！もう少し考えてみてください…
//[Reference] 'I do believe you'd make a wonderful mayor!'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10000900=あなたなら素晴らしい町長になれると信じています！
//[Reference] 'You have a bit more training to go before we ever reach that day, but I hope I can give you the chance!'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10001000=まだ町長になる器ではないですが、立派な町長になれるようにアドバイスをさせてください！
//[Reference] 'That was an excellent harvest festival, was it not?'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10001100=見事な収穫祭でしたよね？
//[Reference] 'I hope we can collaborate on far more festivals in the future!'
staxel.village.character.dialogue.MaxBestFriend.line:10001200=今後も沢山のお祭りに取り組んでいきたいですね！
